Encapsulating side benefits
========================================================
class: small-code

```{r encaps_side, echo=TRUE, eval=FALSE}
boxFancy <- function(box_label,
                x, y, height, width,
                just) {
  pushViewport(
    viewport(x=x, y=y, 
             width=width, height,
             just=just))
  
  grid.rect(gp = gpar(fill="lightyellow"))
  grid.text(box_label,
             gp=gpar(cex=5))
  upViewport()
}

library(grid)
grid.newpage()
box("Some random text",
    x=0.5, y=0.5, 
    width=unit(.8, "npc"), height=unit(.8, "npc"),
    just=c(0.5,0.5))
```

